{"tid":1286924,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"從來未愛你　達哥 可惜我愛懷念　尤其是讓我歡欣的畫面","createTime":"2019-07-05T04:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T15:26:21.000Z","uid":36497,"like":47,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"47c275464e523ae450d950997d7d77ff4da9d70c","tid":1286924,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"達哥也許不會再打機<br />\n大概你的聲線　會抱我造夢<br />\n從前為了不想失約　連女都不敢約<br />\n到哪一天　才回想起　我蠢<br />\n<br />\n和你也許不會再9up<br />\n坐到咖啡酸了　喝也喝不掉<br />\n從前為你捨得課金　寧願零用不要<br />\n談論連場大雨你窗台漏水　不得了<br />\n<br />\n從來未愛你　達哥<br />\n可惜我愛懷念　尤其是讓我歡欣的畫面<br />\n從來未愛你　但永遠為林為華奉獻<br />\n從來沒細心數清楚　一個夏雨天<br />\n一次愉快的睡眠　斷多少髮線"},{"pid":"68aae70fe96646faaed73e968810c58854945799","tid":1286924,"uid":1354,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:14:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />從來未愛你"},{"pid":"3ea83bce4f697938e5158901dd4294c03b9edc0c","tid":1286924,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:14:54.000Z","msg":"达哥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f25acdd8c30647defd862a839dd7d987b10c9fbc","tid":1286924,"uid":13106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"林為華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61bcdad5e49d0c6643f1383f7d60456183619f36","tid":1286924,"uid":52571,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:15:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/EAhQ5ek.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEAhQ5ek.gif&h=bfb86613&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c98c0b5a43d430b52c747ee79344903e82954f4f","tid":1286924,"uid":36497,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"3ea83bce4f697938e5158901dd4294c03b9edc0c","tid":1286924,"uid":886,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-0